headlines.description: — Lamar Jackson returned for the Baltimore Ravens, and so did the chants of “M-V-P!” — on the road.
headlines.shortLinkText: Lamar Jackson torches Miami with 4 TD passes in return from injury and Ravens rout Dolphins 28-6
